quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  7,172,"Era jjukira Mukama omulabiriziwo bwe yajja ku migongo gy’abaana ba Adam ezzadde lyabwe, n’abalagira beeweeko obujulizi, (naagamba nti) Sinze Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe, nebagamba nti, bwe guli, era tukiwaako obujulizi, olwo nno muleme kugamba ku lunaku lw'enkomerero nti, mazima ddala ffe, kino twali tetukimanyi"
  7,173,"Oba muleme kugamba nti, bakadde baffe beebaakola shiriki ffe nga tetunajja, era ffe twali zzadde eryajja oluvanyuma lwabwe. Otuzikiriza otya olw'ebyo ebyakolebwa aboonoonyi"
  7,174,"Era nno bwe tutyo bwe tunnyonnyola e bigambo, babe nga badda (eri okusinza Katonda yekka)"
  7,175,"Era basomere ebikwata ku oyo gwe twawa obubonero bwaffe n'abwesamba, ne Sitane naamunoonya (n'amufuula munne) olwo nno naabeera ow'omu babuze"
  7,176,"Singa twayagala twandimusitudde e ddaala olw'obubonero obwo, naye mazima ddala yye yeemalira ku nsi, era n’agoberera okwagalakwe, olwo nno e kifaananyi kye alinga e mbwa bwogigoba e misinde ewejjawejja, ate nebwogireka eba ewejjawejja, ekyo nno kye kifaananyi kyabo abaalimbisa e bigambo byaffe, bategeeze ebyafaayo kibayambe ku bigambo byaffe, bategeeze ebyafaayo, kibayambe okwefumiitiriza"
  7,177,"Kifaananyi kibi eky’a bantu abaalimbisa e bigambo byaffe, ate nga ekituufu kiri nti emyoyo gyabwe gye baayisanga obubi"
  7,178,"Oyo yenna Katonda gw'aba alungamizza ye y’abeera omulungamu, ate gwabuza, abo nno be baafaafaaganirwa"
  7,179,"Omuliro Jahannama twagutegekera bangi mu majinni ne mu Bantu, (kyova olaba) nti, balina e mitima naye tebagikozesa kutegeera, era balina amaaso gebatalabisa, era balina amatu gebatawuliza, abo nno balinga e bisolo, sinakindi bo b’e babuze okusinga e bisolo, abo nno be beesuulirayo ogwa nnagamba (ku bigambo bye ddiini)"
  7,180,"Era Katonda alina amannya amalungi, kale mugamusabise, era muve kw’abo abakyusakyusa amannyage, balisasulwa ebyo bye baakola"
  7,181,"Mu bantu betwatonda, mulimu e kibiina nga bo bakolera ku mazima, era gebakozesa okukola obwenkanya wakati w’abantu"